title: Candure Dog Lead with Soft Padded and Anti Slip Comfortable Rope Handle, 5 FT Strong Dog Leads, Highly Reflective Dog Leash for Puppy, Medium and Large Dogs
features: Strong and Durable: Our long dog lead is made of high-quality climbing nylon ropes with 1/2-inch diameter, ideally designed for puppy medium and young large dog breeds. We recommend to put this lead on dogs 10-55kg
Soft and Comfy Grip: Black dog lead used EVA-Tech foam padded on handle is super comfortable while dogs pulling and it will protect your hands from being burning

Premium Quality Metal Clips: We used heavy-duty zinc alloy clips, tested to with stand a rapid impact of 400 pounds, 360 degree revolve design ensures that the rope lead does not wrap no matter how the dog moves

Reflective for Safety: Highly reflective threads puppy lead keeps you both safe and visible on your late-evening walks. It can improve the visibility of our dog around the road at night, reduce the risk of injury and protect the safety of the owner

Perfect Length: This 5FT dog rope lead is 152cm long, the dog leashes provides the perfect balance between your control and your dog's freedom. It is able to take a lot of weight and perfectly handles dog leads for small medium and large sized dogs of any breed
